B\in\mathcal{C}
\int_\mathbb{R}I_B(x,y)P_x(dy)=\int_\mathbb{R}\lim_{n\to\infty} I_{B_n}(x,y)P_x(dy)=\lim_{n\to\infty}\int_\mathbb{R}I_{B_n}(x,y)P_x(dy)
\int_A E[I_B(X,Y)\mid X=x]P_x(dx)=\lim_{n\to\infty}\int_A E[I_{B_n}(X,Y)\mid X=x]P_X(dx)=\lim_{n\to\infty}\int_A\int_\mathbb{R}I_{B_n}(x,y)P_x(dy)P_X(dx)=\int_A\int_\mathbb{R}I_{B}(x,y)P_x(dy)P_X(dx)
